org.vadere.simulator.models.ode

Class AbstractModelEquations<T extends DynamicElement>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vadere.simulator.models.ode.AbstractModelEquations<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.commons.math3.ode.FirstOrderDifferentialEquations
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GNMEquations, OVMEquations, SFMEquations

    public abstract class AbstractModelEquations<T extends DynamicElement>
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.apache.commons.math3.ode.FirstOrderDifferentialEquations
    Abstract model equations for an ODE based model of pedestrian motion. Implements the apache FirstOrderDifferentialEquations interface and can thus be used with their integrator methods.
